posting_body: ['About This Home', 'This Stunning rambler w/designer finishes & touches is situated on 1/3 of an acre - corner lot!!', 'You will be minutes from amenities yet tucked away on a quiet, neighborhood street.', 'An open concept design w/ beautiful laminate flooring throughout.', 'Bask in the natural light beaming through the picture windows as you take in the views of the manicured yard.', "Butcher-block style counters adorn the Chef's kitchen w/ appliances ranging from only 6 mos - 2 yrs old.", 'The large Island w/seating is perfect for entertaining.', 'The bonus room is a great flex space & offers access to the fenced-in backyard & patio area.', 'Brand new natural  furnace & Heat pump w/AC, updated baths, large 2-car garage, RV parking & more!', "Don't miss this gem!!", '1969228', 'Move-in timeframe 45 days', 'Dogs and Cats are welcome!', 'House for rent', 'Basic Qualifications:', '★ 620 credit score', '★ $85,000 household income', "★ If the applicants can't meet the requirments listed above, a co-signer with a minimum credit score of 620 and a minimum annual income of 85,000 dollars can help get approval", '★ No evictions', 'No felonies', '★ Min 1 year Lease', 'Text Jing Now for Availability & Application', 'show contact info', '(four two five) 900–8123', '(Respond within 1 hours during working hours)']
